&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gw2skills.net&#x2F;editor&#x2F;?PegAwqlJ0w2abQsGWalOuLftWA-DSRYBRDXwcQ+lRbJQFFgtfLCQoagXDFmBAVA-e&quot;&gt;GW2Skills Link&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;granting-quickness-and-superspeed&quot;&gt;Granting Quickness and Superspeed&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You give quickness through the trait &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2052&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Kinetic Accelerators by performing blast, leap or whirl combos when a field is active.
Your field skills are&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;31248&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Blast Gyro&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;56920&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Function Gyro&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;31167&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spare Capacitor (no superspeed)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Pop your kit fields when lacking before using combos.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Your field gyros provide superspeed but &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;31167&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spare Capacitor does not. If you use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29665&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bypass Coating with &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;31167&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spare Capacitor, it will increase your superspeed uptime and hence increase your DPS.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Essentially if you don&#x27;t want to memorise rotations, if you sweep from right to left (98754321)&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;If you mashed all your field skills and run out of them, you can create one using &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30800&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Elite Mortar Kit, although this is almost never necessary.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Other elite skills can provide additional utility&#x2F;defiance break if you do not require the &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30800&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Elite Mortar Kit.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;You can also use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;56920&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Function Gyro if you have allies that have been downed, and this will summon up to 3 seperate Gyros, which will automatically go revive allies nearby.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;dps-rotation&quot;&gt;DPS Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start this after providing quickness&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5831&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Blowtorch&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;44110&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Refraction Cutter&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto-attack&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;crowd-control&quot;&gt;Crowd Control&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;cc-skills&quot;&gt;CC skills&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;6161&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Throw Mine (used in DPS rotation)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;21661&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Static Shock (AED Toolbelt - backup)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;31167&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Spare Capacitor (CC + Lightning Field)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
